  <body>
    <section name="Assign user to group">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to make a particular user belong to a particular group.</span>

   <script type="text/javascript">
    leftpx=450;
    bottompx=350;
   </script>
   <div class='group'> 
    <div id='screenshot'><div>
     <img src="../../../../images/user_properties.png" alt='Assign user to group screenshot'/>      
   </div></div></div>
   <p>
    Open the list of <a href='./goto_user_properties.html'>properties of the user</a>,
    and on the left, select with the mouse a group from the list of existing groups
    (below the 'new group' button), and drag and drop it to the groups property of the user (low in the list, go below the groups title).
    Unsurprisingly, the user can be assigned to more than one group that way.    
    Then <a href='./save_settings.html'>save the settings</a>.
   </p>

